#OpenKraken-image HOWTO-test

***
Simple test
***

0. Ensure you have the whole libIMAC directory, otherwise you won't have CxxTest.
1. compile and install OpenKraken-image (see HOWTO-build)
2. cd OpenKraken-image/tests/
3. make
4. enjoy \o/
